description:
This is a market on if the price of $UST (TerraUSD) will be above $0.10 in USD on May 23, 2022 (12 PM ET). 

This market will resolve to “Yes” if $UST (TerraUSD) has a candlestick closing price of $0.100001 or more, as per the resolution source, on May 23, 2022, 12 PM ET, and “No” otherwise.

The resolution source for this market will be prices listed on CoinGecko (https://www.coingecko.com/en/coins/terra-usd).

This market will resolve according to the “C” (i.e. closing price) listed for the candle titled “Mon 23 May 2022, 12:00:00”, with the “Price” tab selected, in the Eastern Time Zone. Note, this 12:00:00 candle lists the opening price for 11:30:00 AM ET and the closing price for 12:00:00 PM ET. 

The check will be after the relevant candle closes. If CoinGecko is unavailable, another credible source will be chosen.
